			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">UM6528 PPU is for NTSC-M video standard and should be driven by a crystal of 21.47727Mhz.<br /><br />UM6548 PPU is for PAL-M video standard (as used in Brazil) and should be driven by a crystal of 21.45666Mhz.<br /><br />Both color standards use the same B&amp;W basis TV broadcast system &quot;M&quot; (60Hz).<br /><br />If you use a wrong color crystal on the PPU you will have wrong colors due to difference on signal phase generation at the color information.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
